metadata.name: RFM_Segmentation
metadata.comment: RFM segmentation analysis based on recency, frequency, and monetary values

recency.name: recency
recency.comment: The most recent order date for the user

frequency.name: frequency
frequency.comment: Number of orders placed by the user

monetary.name: monetary
monetary.comment: Total monetary value of orders placed by the user

recency_days.name: recency_days
recency_days.comment: Number of days since the most recent order

recency_score.name: recency_score
recency_score.comment: Score based on the recency of the user's orders

frequency_score.name: frequency_score
frequency_score.comment: Score based on the frequency of the user's orders

monetary_score.name: monetary_score
monetary_score.comment: Score based on the monetary value of the user's orders

segment.comment: Segment of the user based on the RFM score

priority.name: priority
priority.comment: Priority of the user based on the segment
